- The listview is multiselectable (just hold the left mouse button down and
  move the mouse). This is useful to quote part of the message: select the
  wanted rows and then remember to enable quoting when the message write
  window appears.

- The listview can be scrolled using the up/down cursor keys; shift +
  up/down scrolls one page at a time.

